  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK817">
<l>nakaivakaiya rākiya naṭpiṟ pakaivarāṟ </l>
<l>pattaṭutta kōṭi yuṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What comes from enemies is a hundred million times more profitable than what comes from the friendship of those who cause only laughter.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
